{
  "text": "It has been shown in [CITATION_1] how a binary reduction (see [CITATION_2] ) can be used to parallelize this computation. A binary reduction uses a combining operation on two maps L i and L j to derive the combined map L i, j as depicted in Eq. [CITATION_3] .",
